
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "B2BTraining";
}

<style>
    html, body {
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    .custom-heading {
        font-size: 2.5rem; /* نفس حجم الـ h1 الافتراضي */
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 576px) {
        .responsive-btn {
            width: 400px !important; /* حجم أصغر للموبايل */
            font-size: 13px !important; /* خط أصغر */
            padding: 8px 12px !important; /* تقليل الـ padding */
        }
        /* جعل الأزرار في النص */
        .buttons-container {
            flex-direction: column !important; /* ترتيب عمودي على الموبايل */
            align-items: center !important; /* توسيط العناصر أفقيًا */
        }
    }
    /* يظهر فقط في الموبايل */
    @@media (max-width: 767px) {
        .mobile-break

    {
        display: inline;
    }

    h2.custom-heading span {
        white-space: normal !important; /* عشان يسمح بالنزول للسطر */
        font-size: 24px !important; /* تصغير الخط في الموبايل */
    }

    }

    .section-title {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .check-item::before {
        content: "☑ ";
        color: #000;
    }

    ul.custom-list {
        list-style-type: disc;
        margin-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight {
        color: #0056b3;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .feature {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 50%), url(../img/B2BTraining-down.png) left center no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: left center;
        min-height: 500px; /* ارتفاع مناسب */
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        border-radius: 10px; /* لو حابب تضيف حواف ناعمة */
    }

    .logo {
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
    }

</style>


<div class="position-relative text-center">
    <img class="w-100" style="object-fit:cover;" src="~/img/B2BTraining.png" alt="Image">

    <!-- النص فوق الصورة (أسفل يسار) -->
    <div class="position-absolute bottom-0 start-0 w-100 text-start p-4">
        <h1 class="fw-bold display-4 mb-3" style="color:white">B2BTraining</h1>
    </div>
</div>




<div class="container my-5">

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h5 class="section-title">Your Team Has Potential  We Turn It into Exceptional Performance.</h5>
        <p class="check-item">In a hyper-competitive market, the smartest investment is in the minds that drive your business. We don't offer conventional training courses; we design customized learning experiences that build skills, foster leadership, and guarantee a tangible return on your human capital investment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h5 class="section-title">Are You Facing One of These Challenges in Your Company?</h5>
       
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h5 class="section-title">You know your team is the engine of your success, but you might be noticing signs of skill gaps that are hindering growth</h5>

        <ul class="custom-list">
            <li><strong>A Leadership Gap:</strong> Are your first-line managers struggling to motivate their teams or manage performance effectively?</li>
            <li><strong>A Technical Skills Deficit:</strong> Do new technologies or quality standards in your sector (especially Pharma & Food) require specialized technical skills your team lacks?</li>
            <li><strong>Decreased Productivity:</strong> Do you feel that processes could be more efficient and that your team could achieve more with the same resources?</li>
            <li><strong>Difficulty Adapting:</strong> Does your team find it hard to adapt to rapid market changes or adopt new ways of working?</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>






<hr class="mb-5" />






<div class="container py-5">

    <!-- Section Header -->
