        <h5 class="section-title"> Why Our Training Makes a Difference: It's Built on Quality and Reality.</h5>
        <h6 class="highlight">At Resources One, we believe effective training must be more than just information; it must be a transformational experience. Here’s how we guarantee it:</h6>
