            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Thomas Section -->
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="~/img/thomas.jpg" alt="Thomas Logo" class="logo img-fluid">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h6 class="highlight">Deep Sector-Specific Expertise: Specialists in Pharma & Food Industries</h6>
            <p>
                We don't offer generic training. We speak your industry's language. Whether it's Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP), the latest Quality Assurance techniques, or specialized sales skills for pharmaceutical companies, our programs are designed to meet the precise challenges and opportunities of your sector.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <img src="~/img/thomas.jpg" alt="Thomas Logo" class="logo img-fluid">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h6 class="highlight">An Integrated Approach: Training as Part of a Success Ecosystem</h6>
            <p>
                We are not just a training company; we are an integrated HR consultancy. This means we link training directly to the results of competency assessments and help you measure the impact of training on actual performance, ensuring every training hour contributes to your business goals.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>










